    <!-- http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Hepatic_AcTox -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Hepatic_AcTox">
        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D#Toxicity_Data"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Presence of at least one of these CTCAE definitions:

1.Alanine aminotransferase increased
G1: &gt;ULN - 3.0 x ULN 
G2: &gt;3.0 - 5.0 x ULN 
G3: &gt;5.0 - 20.0 x ULN 
G4: &gt;20.0 x ULN
G5: not reported

2.Alkaline phosphatase increased
G1: &gt;ULN - 2.5 x ULN 
G2: &gt;2.5 - 5.0 x ULN 
G3: &gt;5.0 - 20.0 x ULN 
G4: &gt;20.0 x ULN
G5: Not reported

3.Aspartate aminotransferase increased
G1: &gt;ULN - 3.0 x ULN 
G2: &gt;3.0 - 5.0 x ULN 
G3: &gt;5.0 - 20.0 x ULN 
G4: &gt;20.0 x ULN
G5: Not reported

4.Blood bilirubin increased
G1: &gt;ULN - 1.5 x ULN 
G2: &gt;1.5 - 3.0 x ULN 
G3: &gt;3.0 - 10.0 x ULN 
G4: &gt;10.0 x ULN
G5: Not reported

5.GGT increased
G1: &gt;ULN - 2.5 x ULN 
G2: &gt;2.5 - 5.0 x ULN 
G3: &gt;5.0 - 20.0 x ULN 
G4: &gt;20.0 x ULN
G5: Not reported</obo:IAO_0000115>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Infection_AcTox -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Infection_AcTox">
        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D#Toxicity_Data"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A disorder characterized by an inflammatory or infectious process involving the larynx, lips, lymph nodes, trachea, salivary glands, etc.

G3: IV antibiotic, antifungal, or antiviral intervention indicated; radiologic or operative intervention indicated
G4: Life-threatening consequences; urgent intervention indicated
G5: Death</obo:IAO_0000115>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Medullary_AcTox -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Medullary_AcTox">
        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D#Toxicity_Data"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Presence of at least one of these CTCAE definitions:

1.White blood cell decreased
G1: &lt;LLN - 3000/mm3; &lt;LLN - 3.0 x 10^9 /L
G2: &lt;3000 - 2000/mm3; &lt;3.0 - 2.0 x 10^9 /L
G3: &lt;2000 - 1000/mm3; &lt;2.0 - 1.0 x 10^9 /L
G4: &lt;1000/mm3; &lt;1.0 x 10^9 /L
G5: Not reported

2.Neutrophil count decreased
G1: &lt;LLN - 1500/mm3; &lt;LLN - 1.5 x 10^9 /L
G2: &lt;1500 - 1000/mm3; &lt;1.5 - 1.0 x 10^9 /L
G3: &lt;1000 - 500/mm3; &lt;1.0 - 0.5 x 10^9 /L
G4: &lt;500/mm3; &lt;0.5 x 10^9 /L
G5: Not reported

3.Platelet count decreased
G1: &lt;LLN - 75,000/mm3; &lt;LLN - 75.0 x 10^9 /L
G2: &lt;75,000 - 50,000/mm3; &lt;75.0 - 50.0 x 10^9 /L
G3: &lt;50,000 - 25,000/mm3; &lt;50.0 - 25.0 x 10^9 /L
G4: &lt;25,000/mm3; &lt;25.0 x 10^9/L
G5: Not reported

4.Anemia 
G1: Hemoglobin (Hgb) &lt;LLN - 10.0 g/dL; &lt;LLN - 6.2 mmol/L; &lt;LLN - 100 g/L
G2: Hgb &lt;10.0 - 8.0 g/dL; &lt;6.2 - 4.9 mmol/L; &lt;100 - 80g/L 
G3: Hgb &lt;8.0 g/dL; &lt;4.9 mmol/L; &lt;80 g/L; transfusion indicated
G4: Life-threatening consequences; urgent intervention indicated
G5: Death</obo:IAO_0000115>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Mucositis_AcTox -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Mucositis_AcTox">
        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D#Toxicity_Data"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Oral: A disorder characterized by inflammation of the oral mucosal.
G3: Severe pain; interfering with oral intake
G4: Life-threatening consequences; urgent intervention indicated
G5: Death

Laryngeal: A disorder characterized by an inflammation involving the mucous membrane of the larynx
G3: Severe pain; severely altered eating/swallowing; medical intervention indicated
G4: Life-threatening airway compromise; urgent intervention indicated (e.g., tracheotomy or intubation)
G5: Death

Pharyngeal: A disorder characterized by an inflammation involving the mucous membrane of the pharynx.
G3: Severe pain; unable to adequately aliment or hydrate orally; limiting self-care ADL
G4: Life-threatening consequences; urgent intervention indicated
G5: Death

Tracheal: A disorder characterized by an inflammation involving the mucous membrane of the trachea.
G3: Severe pain; hemorrhage or respiratory symptoms; limiting self-care ADL
G4: Life-threatening consequences; urgent intervention indicated
G5: Death</obo:IAO_0000115>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Pain_Toxicity_12 -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Pain_Toxicity_12">
        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D#Toxicity_Data"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A disorder characterized by the sensation of distress, agony or marked discomfort in a lymph node, mouth, tongue or lips.

G3: Severe pain; limiting self care ADL (Activities of Daily Living)
G4: Grade not available
G5: Grade not available</obo:IAO_0000115>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Pain_Toxicity_24 -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Pain_Toxicity_24">
        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D#Toxicity_Data"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A disorder characterized by the sensation of distress, agony or marked discomfort in a lymph node, mouth, tongue or lips.

G3: Severe pain; limiting self care ADL (Activities of Daily Living)
G4: Grade not available
G5: Grade not available</obo:IAO_0000115>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Pain_Toxicity_6 -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Pain_Toxicity_6">
        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D#Toxicity_Data"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A disorder characterized by the sensation of distress, agony or marked discomfort in a lymph node, mouth, tongue or lips.

G3: Severe pain; limiting self care ADL (Activities of Daily Living)
G4: Grade not available
G5: Grade not available</obo:IAO_0000115>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Renal_AcTox -->

    <owl:Class rdf:about="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/tox#Renal_AcTox">
        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D#Toxicity_Data"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>CTCAE: Acute kidney injury.

G1: Creatinine level increase of &gt;0.3 mg/dL; creatinine 1.5 - 2.0 x above baseline
G2: Creatinine 2 - 3 x above baseline 
G3: Creatinine &gt;3 x baseline or &gt;4.0 mg/dL; hospitalization indicated
G4: Life-threatening consequences; dialysis indicated
G5: Death</obo:IAO_0000115>
    </owl:Class>
    


