    <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://ontology.lst.tfo.upm.es/BD2D/patho#TNM_pN_8Edition_Oropharynx_p16Positive@@3">
        <rdfs:comment>Metastasis in 4 or fewer lymph nodes</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>N1</rdfs:label>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>Alphanumeric code of the TNM classification system (8th Edition) which in this case indicates that the oropharynx cancer (p16-Positive) has spread to 4 or fewer lymph nodes.</obo:IAO_0000115>
